title: Worlds
description: The sculpture measures 30x15x45 cm and is made of oak wood.
context: The sculpture measures 30x15x45 cm and is made of oak wood. Characteristic are the straight lines and irregular planes. Within these planes, three figures are situated. A starfish, a reptile, and a human: three different worlds that tell the story of evolution.
